otherwise known as the tire’s maximum load-carrying capacity measured in Kilos (KGs) or Pounds (LBS)","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"173– this is the load index of the tire or otherwise known as the tire’s maximum load-carrying capacity measured in Kilos (KGs) or Pounds (LBS)","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-813d-ae92-f840f2a1a6bc","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-810d-986e-d46c31bab912"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:02:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:02:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"bulleted_list_item","bulleted_list_item":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"D – or D ratings stand for the speed category of the tire. This letter will change per speed category and can be broken down by the below table:","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"D – or D ratings stand for the speed category of the tire. This letter will change per speed category and can be broken down by the below table:","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8113-9016-e83a88f53a87","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-810d-986e-d46c31bab912"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:02:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:02:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"image","image":{"caption":[],"type":"external","external":{"url":"https://maxamtire.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/speed-category-ch